oji\" />"},{"pid":"22fa77211c99a39592097925d9dc7f45519e4f90","tid":1635180,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:29:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23dd4f9e4877ea067d34007ff5fcb0a9339b41ee","tid":1635180,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:29:40.000Z","msg":"【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上為節錄內容，覺得有道理請睇全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a>"},{"pid":"21f37b914f45f4ad5bd180f6ad65166d9d7ad793","tid":1635180,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23795a3740ad9c1e3a30ff0abdf20d42d9d33967","tid":1635180,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:34:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66327d54a57d328664f50cc47e826a27d83c1085","tid":1635180,"uid":160842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:34:52.000Z","msg":"勿拆黨鐵！！全民被罷工！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n罷工係對個政權最撚有衝擊既抗爭手法，但三罷做左咁撚多次，都係得8.5成功，因為計劃左好撚耐，對香港人黎講，個個都只想被罷工，到呢個地步，你仲想做休息撚，而唔乘勝追擊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三樣香港人應同樣憎恨既野：<br />\n政府、黑警、黨鐵<br />\n<br />\n呢三樣先係主線<br />\n你個啲乜鳩紅藍店，我理撚得你幾時搞？<br />\n個啲要休息，冇問題，但咁撚樣都唔食住上，令到全港自動罷工，咁我真係代表我全力支持既香港政府多謝你為香港既經濟服務<br />\n<br />\n唔撚係話和理非冇用，但勇和齊上齊落唔撚得？"},{"pid":"489c87e11ec6b04d1121226cea3e21c4e3bdcd36","tid":1635180,"uid":100337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T12:37:57.000Z","msg":"裝修黨鐵最有效"}]}